   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Fiji Support Programme</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This programme seeks to provide &#xA3;1.7M of International Climate Finance (ICF) funding for ODA-eligible activities in support of the Fijian Presidency of the UNFCCC climate negotiations in 2017-2018. The programme of activities proposed to fund will include capacity-building for the Fijian government, support to the Fijians&#x2019; Pre-COP event in October, and a series of technical workshops at the Pre-COP, COP and Bonn inter-sessional events, on issues important to Fiji, SIDS and the UK.</narrative>
  </description>
